{"tid":1970202,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》製作人影片細節暗示 PC 版本的存在？","createTime":"2020-04-13T03:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T04:44:21.000Z","uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4661ae60622b0dddeb146f968c8d72d2ae20b282","tid":1970202,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:34:11.000Z","msg":"Square Enix 正式推出《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》後，製作人北瀨佳範公開了「對粉絲的上市訊息」影片，然而影片中的小細節卻讓玩家猜測是否在暗示，未來《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》PC 版的來臨。<br />\n <br />\n  《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》是 1997 年 1 月在初代 PlayStation 主機上推出、全球累計銷售超過千萬套的經典 RPG《Final Fantasy VII》相隔 23 年後的完全重製版，在這波「對粉絲的上市訊息」影片中，遊戲畫面下方寫著「Gameplay captured on PC」，而畫面右上方除了「PS4 獨家」外下方還有小字寫著「在 PS4 平台上最先玩到（Available First on PS4）」，而引發眼尖的玩家討論。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/54/c6aaf0e0923002907f5aebc0e5189k65.PNG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F54%2Fc6aaf0e0923002907f5aebc0e5189k65.PNG%3Fw%3D1000&h=7fbfd24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  有的玩家認為，這樣的訊息可能暗示說存在著一個《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》PC 版本，但到底僅是 Square Enix 內部的開發版本，還是未來正式會推出在 PC 平台上，則有待官方未來證實是否真有此事。<br />\n <br />\n  先前海外媒體曾揭露《Final Fantasy VII 重製版》將於 PlayStation 4 限時獨佔一年，因此 PlayStation 4 的限時獨佔期間至少會到 2021 年 4 月 10 日。"},{"pid":"10a49ce6a251776280d8831a64cd260ebebbf993","tid":1970202,"uid":117405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"PC玩家好撚慘...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fdf8d3b5bc7ba53c3047f0ba945adf0d08183a","tid":1970202,"uid":184827,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10a49ce6a251776280d8831a64cd260ebebbf993","tid":1970202,"uid":117405,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"PC玩家好撚慘...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"鬼叫咁多翻版咩"},{"pid":"7dbdbf6a46e09ab56